" your environment (e.g., `0,1,2,3` for 4 chips)."
msgstr ""
"`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`：必须设置为分配给您的环境的NPU芯片ID（例如，4个芯片设置为`0,1,2,3`）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:259
msgid ""
"`--port`: adjust to avoid conflicts with other services running on the "
"same machine."
msgstr ""
