#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:378
msgid "8 Performance Evaluation"
msgstr "8 性能评估"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:382
msgid ""
"For setup details, please refer to [Using AISBench for performance "
"evaluation](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation)."
msgstr "设置详情请参考[使用AISBench进行性能评估](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-performance-evaluation)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:384
msgid ""
"First, configure the model for streaming performance testing "
"(`ais_bench/benchmark/configs/models/vllm_api/vllm_api_stream_chat.py`):"
msgstr "首先，配置模型用于流式性能测试（`ais_bench/benchmark/configs/models/vllm_api/vllm_api_stream_chat.py`）："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:414
msgid ""
"Key differences from the accuracy config: `stream=True`, "
"`ignore_eos=True` (ensures output reaches `max_out_len` for consistent "
"TPOT measurement), and `batch_size` controls concurrency."
msgstr "与精度配置的主要区别：`stream=True`、`ignore_eos=True`（确保输出达到 `max_out_len` 以进行一致的TPOT测量），以及 `batch_size` 控制并发数。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:416
msgid ""
"Then, configure the synthetic dataset distribution "
"(`ais_bench/datasets/synthetic/synthetic_config.py`). Adjust the "
"configuration based on your actual scenario. Note that random synthetic "
"data is not suitable for benchmarking scenarios where prefix caching is "
"enabled, as random inputs produce zero cache hit rate."
msgstr "然后，配置合成数据集分布（`ais_bench/datasets/synthetic/synthetic_config.py`）。根据实际场景调整配置。注意，随机合成数据不适用于启用前缀缓存的基准测试场景，因为随机输入会产生零缓存命中率。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:435
msgid "Then run the performance evaluation:"
msgstr "然后运行性能评估："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:441
msgid ""
"The `--models` value should match the `abbr` in your model config file. "
"Use `--num-prompts` to limit the number of test requests."
msgstr "`--models` 值应与模型配置文件中的 `abbr` 匹配。使用 `--num-prompts` 限制测试请求数量。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:443
msgid "Using vLLM Benchmark"
msgstr "使用vLLM基准测试"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:445
msgid ""
"Refer to [vLLM benchmark](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/) "
"for more details."
msgstr "更多详情请参考[vLLM基准测试](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:447
msgid ""
"Take the `serve` subcommand as an example. The `--random-output-len` "
"parameter controls the number of output tokens per request; adjust it "
"based on your target scenario (e.g., 2048 for short outputs, 32768 for "
"long outputs)."
msgstr "以 `serve` 子命令为例。`--random-output-len` 参数控制每个请求的输出token数；根据目标场景调整（例如短输出用2048，长输出用32768）。"

